he.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292f582a3c78ee215f75174adcf72ca4bc3d755a","tid":2018152,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:13:14.000Z","msg":"此告急文宣絕對係廣告，自費架屌你！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2018306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2018306</a>"},{"pid":"5c5915afb7f1b2cca9c4addd4b404c8a3ce93295","tid":2018152,"uid":37389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"81bb0b476761fd9db34b12a3138d09fd5a3c0818","tid":2018152,"uid":46504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T13:47:55.000Z","msg":"推呀 有冇人可以draft 一個出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:18:27.000Z","msg":"Dear Career Center,<br />\n<br />\nI am writing to express my concern about the captioned recruitment advertisement posted on the career centre website of your University. <br />\n<br />\nDuring the past year, Hong Kong Police Force has clearly demonstrated that they are not an ethical employer, by allowing their employees to engage in various brutal acts during many public events in Hong Kong and refusing to conduct any follow ups regarding complaints on the misbehavior of their employees. Some of these behaviors, including attacking a toddler with pepper spray, which was clearing filmed by the media, were as disgusting as some notorious war crimes. <br />\n<br />\nThe University of Toronto is a reputable University, partnering with an unethical employer would eventually damage your reputation. Although providing various job opportunities to your students is very important, encouraging them to work at an institution which does not value human rights is still not a good idea.<br />\n<br />\nI hope the Career Center could withdraw the recruitment advertisement of the Hong Kong Police Force.